s own hobbies include bowling fishing and golf Although Commissioner Bruhn has only held office since Nov 1996 he sees a bright future ahead for St Lucie County and hopes to make a positive difference for its citizens mailto pentzj co st lucie fl us E Mail John Bruhn 
